description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit Band 2 Healthcare Assistants to join our nursing team for our 17 bedded ward at Stratton Community Hospital. This role will require the post holder to be committed to the on-going development of the ward and multi disciplinary team working, aiming to deliver the highest standards of patient care to our predominantly elderly patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Full and part time posts available undertaking a range of Early, Late and Night duties on a rotational basis in order to support 24 hour nursing care, 7 days per week. Although based at Stratton Community Hospital, a flexible working approach is required to support Launceston Community Hospital as service needs require.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fixed term post until 30th April 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJacqueline HiggittJob titleWard SisterTelephone number01288 320103&lt;/p&gt;
